channel.title: Need Help With My Compiler.bat
channel.description:
Hey, I'm using JDK version 1 and the server source is CheezScape PK 78. Every time I put on my compiler it comes up with this message: [code]Note: stream.java uses or overides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
This is what is there when go on edit: [code]@echo off title CheezScape Compiler javac *.java pause[/code]
Any help will be greatly appreciated, this is going to be the first server I properly edit. Please help, Thanks
Sithling
